data.description: Hello Everyone! Come see this beautiful detached 2 Family, 2,358 sqft home with 3 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom in each apartment with a fully finished basement all new appliances that were installed just a few years ago. Also a new Roof that was finished 6 years ago. this magnificent Multi-Family is very desirable for anyone looking to live and collect rental income. each apartment can easily be Rented for $3,500 with even the possibility of converting the  living room to a possible bedroom on the First FL and utilizing the nice size dining room as a living room. while Landlord can live on ground level this opportunity is defiantly great  to live and save at the same time. the additional units will offset the amount paid on mortgage this is priced to sell brand new boilers just installed this year also new roof that was finished 6 years ago and also lots of the storage space throughout the house. this is a turn-key ready.
